name: Villa Nugraha Private Pool
address: Anturan, Buleleng, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81119, Indonesia
review 1: We had the most lovely time here. The villa is spacious, extremely clean and kept very well. The kitchen is fully equipped, the pool clean and the garden is full of flowers and plants. The owners of the villa were lovely and kind, and made sure our stay went perfectly. Cannot recommend it enough
review 2: Great relaxing stay. Lovely beach. Kids had a great time snorkelling, dolphin watching
review 3: A new and privately owned villa in Lovina. The owners are very kind! It was my birthday during my stay at the villa and they visited me and brought a chocolate pie. You can either rent the villa with one or two bedrooms. The villa also has a fully-equipped kitchen, a private swimming pool and private parking area. We stayed for 1 week, but wished we could stay longer.
